\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0- Size: ~1.2GB for 2.8M triples
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 Pros:
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0- Single row per kernel version
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0- JSONB query operators for simple lookups
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 Cons:
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0- Cannot perform SPARQL queries
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0- No semantic reasoning
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0- Graph traversal extremely slow
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 ```
\f1\fs24 \
\

