\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - PostgreSQL handles metadata + governance (what it's designed for)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - Neo4j handles runtime queries (what it's designed for)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - Each tool optimized for its specific purpose
